pseudocode for a vending machine:

select item to be purchased

insert cash 

CASE 1: cash < item value 
item value - money = balance 
prompt "insert" balance 
'break' 

CASE 2: cash > item value 
cash - item value = change 
eject item 
eject change 
'break' 

CASE 3: cash = item value 
eject item 
'break' 

CASE 4: select cancel 
eject cash 

CASE 5: machine not working
eject cash
display message "Machine not working"

END
